data.description:
Beautiful White Horse Beach Pond Front Townhouse with ocean views available for Rent May 6, 2019.
2 Bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, living room, spacious kitchen with eat in dining area, large rear deck overlooking a lake and views of the Atlantic from your front door. 3 levels of spacious living featuring gleaming hardwood floors, a gas fireplace, full house fan, and much great natural light. Private one car garage and extra parking available for a second car and guests. Live across the street from the Beach! This is a great location right off Taylor Avenue in Plymouth - minutes from Routes 3 and 3a, Plymouth center, and the Cape Cod Canal. 45 minutes to Boston and close to the Plymouth and Kingston Commuter Rail Stations. Call or email to schedule a showing.
